<li><h3>Did it perform to your expectations?</h3>
<p>Yes, Node.js performed well beyond our expectations. At first we did not quite get our progran to host, but once we got a grasp on the Node.js framework, it become easier for us to host our program as well as learn quite a bit about Node.js and its' programming.
</p>
